column6: "A PLAGUE OF LOCUSTS" Concludes! As the final secrets of the radical Locust Project are revealed, Johnny must save hundreds of innocent lives ... AND find a way to undo the changes caused by the insidious project! 32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99
